# TASK TO DO
1. Add basic aunthentication to it. unAunthenticated users will not have access to the enpoint
2. create a new entity of student and each student has a course assigned to him or her or list of course he or she offers
3. give an Authority to this student, only student that has right  to the course can view there course they have right to.
4. create a new entity call Course which will have list of subjects that belongs to the course
5. Create a subjects entity with there respective properties
6. create a controller that create a course with it's respective properties, add a subject or list of subjects to the course, disable a subject or remove it from the course,
update the subject, and also update the course.
7. write unit test for this projects and run your tests against your code.
8. also test your endpoint with postman

8. please ask questions if you need clearer view.

# What you will learn after the project
1. You will learn how JDBC and hibernate interract in database
2. hands-on experience with spring boot and postreqs
3. basic crud operation
4. how authentication works.
